channel.title: GreenHaven International Prison - [Beta Release] [Drugs] [Prison Server]
channel.description:
Server Address: Play.GreenHavenPrison.com
GreenHaven is a prison server, where you earn money to rankup. Ranks are: - D-Prisoner - C-Prisoner - B-Prisoner - A-Prisoner - X-Prisoner - Free
Each time you rankup, the block gets better, the mines have more ore in them, and there is less people around.
For more info please visit: www.bit.ly/GreenHaven Website: www.bit.ly/GreenHavenWebsite
